Package: bioFlex
Type: Package
Title: Estimation and model selection for strictly positive heavy tailed data, using flexible parametric distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shakeel Gavioli-Akilagun
Maintainer: Shakeel Gavioli-Akilagun <shakeel.gavioli@googlemail.com>
Description: Maximum likelihood estimation of flexible parametric distributions nested by the Generalized Beta distribution of the Second Kind, model selection via various information criterations; 
              procedures for estimating the conditional mean E(Y|X) and conditional probability P(Y>k |X) of a response variable; 
              Cholesky decomposition to correlate estimated parameters.
License: GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE (Version 3)
Depends:bbmle, extraDistr, broom, VGAM, actuar, DescTools
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
